# Node.js — Test Patterns (generic)

## Stack context
- Node.js 18+ LTS
- Test runner: Jest hoặc Vitest (chọn 1, ghi rõ trong project-context.yaml `test_runner:`)
- Run: `npm test` hoặc `npx jest` / `npx vitest run`

## Phân loại test

| Cần test gì | Tool | Ghi chú |
|---|---|---|
| Pure function / Service logic | Jest/Vitest unit | Mock repository ở boundary |
| HTTP endpoint | supertest + app instance | Mock service hoặc test DB |
| Repository + DB | integration test | Test DB riêng hoặc container |

## Unit test (service)
```javascript
describe('CourseService', () => {
  it('should_returnCourse_when_idExists', async () => {
    const repo = { findById: jest.fn().mockResolvedValue({ id: 1 }) };
    const service = new CourseService(repo);
    const result = await service.getById(1);
    expect(result.id).toBe(1);
  });
});
```

## HTTP test (supertest)
```javascript
const request = require('supertest');
const app = require('../app');

it('should_return401_when_tokenInvalid', async () => {
  await request(app).get('/api/courses').set('Authorization', 'Bearer bad').expect(401);
});
```

## Test naming convention
```
should_{expected_behavior}_when_{condition}
```

## Mock chỉ ở boundary
- Mock: Repository, Redis, external HTTP, queue producer
- KHÔNG mock: Service gọi Service nội bộ cùng module (dùng integration test)

## Traceability in tests
Đăng ký test case vào file trace TSV (cột `verifies_tag`) dưới dạng `<đường_dẫn_test>::<tên_test>` (ví dụ: `tests/assignment.test.js::should_createAssignment_when_inputsValid`). Không ghi trace comment trực tiếp vào mã nguồn.

## Run commands
- All tests: `npm test`
- Single file: `npm test -- path/to/file.test.js`
- Coverage: `npm test -- --coverage`
